                            <comment id="16198932" author="yuzhihong@gmail.com" created="Tue, 10 Oct 2017 16:38:23 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Looking at core/src/main/scala/kafka/server/DelayedDeleteRecords.scala :&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
          &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;case&lt;/span&gt; Some(partition) =&amp;gt;
            &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; (partition eq ReplicaManager.OfflinePartition) {
              (&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;false&lt;/span&gt;, Errors.KAFKA_STORAGE_ERROR, DeleteRecordsResponse.INVALID_LOW_WATERMARK)
            } &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;else&lt;/span&gt; {
              partition.leaderReplicaIfLocal match {
                &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;case&lt;/span&gt; Some(_) =&amp;gt;
                  val leaderLW = partition.lowWatermarkIfLeader
                  (leaderLW &amp;gt;= status.requiredOffset, Errors.NONE, leaderLW)
                &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;case&lt;/span&gt; None =&amp;gt;
                  (&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;false&lt;/span&gt;, Errors.NOT_LEADER_FOR_PARTITION, DeleteRecordsResponse.INVALID_LOW_WATERMARK)
              }
            }
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;It seems NOT_LEADER_FOR_PARTITION is covered.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="16198963" author="tombentley" created="Tue, 10 Oct 2017 16:56:58 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;It &lt;em&gt;would be&lt;/em&gt; covered if execution ever got this far. In fact &lt;tt&gt;ReplicaManager.deleteRecordsOnLocalLog()&lt;/tt&gt; has already thrown &lt;tt&gt;UnknownTopicOrPartitionException&lt;/tt&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
